title: Domantas Šimkus
text:
Domantas Šimkus (born 10 February 1996) is a <a href="Lithuania">Lithuania</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="S%C9%99bail%20FK">Səbail FK</a>.
International.
He made his <a href="Lithuania%20national%20football%20team">Lithuania national football team</a> debut on 17 November 2018 in a <a href="2018%E2%80%9319%20UEFA%20Nations%20League%20C">2018–19 UEFA Nations League C</a> game against <a href="Romania%20national%20football%20team">Romania</a>.
